This is a Qt program that lazily ports CuckyDev's IntTool to a GUI for beginner usage.

![screenshot](https://private-user-images.githubusercontent.com/83806269/463451282-2fa88b4a-71ef-4286-863f-ac48344bf6f3.png?jwt=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..gGXlwFK_XBYBS8YVzV3jofggPGpM4emJNNDSrr3M5aA)

Tutorial:

To import, select a INT file from a PaRappa The Rapper 1 ISO and then select a folder to unpack the files into.
To export, select a .txt generated from the output, then save the output.
